                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right mb-4 md:mb-0">
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-display-elegant font-bold text-renaissance-maroon mb-2">Early Renaissance</h3>
                                <p class="text-renaissance-gold font-medium mb-3">c. 1400–1490</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">Characterized by the rediscovery of classical antiquity, development of linear perspective, and emphasis on humanism.</p>
                                <div class="mt-4">
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mr-2">Giotto</span>
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mr-2">Masaccio</span>
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Botticelli</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
                            <div class="timeline-dot w-8 h-8 bg-renaissance-gold rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg mx-auto"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="timeline-item flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 order-2 md:order-1">
                            <div class="timeline-dot w-8 h-8 bg-renaissance-gold rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg mx-auto"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 order-1 md:order-2 mb-4 md:mb-0">
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-display-elegant font-bold text-renaissance-maroon mb-2">High Renaissance</h3>
                                <p class="text-renaissance-gold font-medium mb-3">c. 1490–1527</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">The peak of Renaissance art, marked by harmony, balance, and the idealization of beauty. Centered in Rome and Florence.</p>
                                <div class="mt-4">
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mr-2">Da Vinci</span>
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mr-2">Michelangelo</span>
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">Raphael</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="timeline-item flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right mb-4 md:mb-0">
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-display-elegant font-bold text-renaissance-maroon mb-2">Late Renaissance & Mannerism</h3>
                                <p class="text-renaissance-gold font-medium mb-3">c. 1520–1600</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">Characterized by artificiality, elegance, and emotional intensity, moving away from classical balance toward more expressive forms.</p>
                                <div class="mt-4">
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mr-2">Titian</span>
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm mr-2">Tintoretto</span>
                                    <span class="inline-block bg-renaissance-cream text-renaissance-velvet px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">El Greco</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12">
                            <div class="timeline-dot w-8 h-8 bg-renaissance-gold rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg mx-auto"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
